Package: detlimitr3
Title: Estimation of detection limits using R using S3
Version: 0.0.1.00
Author: Peter Watkins   
Maintainer: Peter Watkins <Peter.Watkins@csiro.au>
Description: A set of functions for estimating detection limits of calibration data, using S3.
    The package can be used for linear, quadratic or power regression. In the case of
    linear regression, the detection limits are estimated using three approaches; i) Miller & Miller, ii 
    Vogelgesang & HÃ¤drich, and iii) Hubert & Vos (by iteration).
Imports:
    dplyr, 
    ggplot2, 
    ggtrendline,
    minpack.lm,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat
